<li>Cost: $15-30 per tile + labor ($100-200 service call)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Example scenario:</strong></p>
<p>Branch falls on roof, breaking 5 tiles:</p>
<p><strong>Repair cost:</strong> $200-300 (replace 5 tiles + service call)</p>
<p><strong>Same branch on shingle roof:</strong></p>
<p><strong>Repair cost:</strong> $800-1,500 (replace entire damaged section)</p>
